  "time_ut": 1656910851,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An underworld gang member was killed in police firing",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Joseph Kumara, who is said to be an underworld gang member, was killed in a shootout with the police in Gampaha, Bemmulla area this morning (4th), police said.",
        "The police have identified him as a 41-year-old resident of Dargatown, Alpitiya who had served in the army for some time.",
        "When a group of officers from the Colombo Crime Investigation Division raided the house early this morning on a tip-off that he was in a house in the Ulagama area under the Gampaha police jurisdiction, it was found that his motorcycle overturned near Bemmulla, Bandarabatawala Velaya while the police officers were chasing him after he fled on a motorcycle. The police said that Joseph was shot and killed when the police officers overturned and shot at the van in which the police officers were traveling with a firearm that he had in his hand.",
        "A T-56 type firearm and an ammunition bag containing live bullets have been taken into police custody and the van in which the police officers were traveling has been damaged by the gunfire, the police say.",
        "Regarding this incident, as per the instructions of Mr. Deshbandu, Senior DIG in charge of Western Province, under the supervision of Mr. Mahinda Dissanayake, DIG in charge of Western Province, North and Mr. Indika De Silva, Senior Superintendent of Police in charge of Gampaha Division, Bemmulla Police is conducting further investigations under the direction of Gampaha Assistant Superintendent of Police, Mr. Thusitha Kumara. Meanwhile, the magistrate's inquest was scheduled to be held."
      ],
